15
00:03:00,055 --> 00:03:01,682
Éteins tout de suite.

16
00:03:01,765 --> 00:03:03,100
Éteins ça !

17
00:03:03,183 --> 00:03:05,143
Y a rien de choquant.

18
00:03:05,227 --> 00:03:07,312
Ça parle d'un meurtre.

19
00:03:07,688 --> 00:03:13,235
